      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 23 picture captions about self-taught artists, which misspelled Joe Ruffilo's name and which misstated title of work by Robert Bonnano (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption last Sunday with an article about self-taught artists misspelled the surname of one from Paterson. He is Joe Ruffilo, not Rufilo. Another caption misstated the title of a work by Robert Bonnano of Newark. It is Mount Pita, not Mount Peter.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
